Name: Frosty Kiss
About the game: It's been a year since Semyon returned from 'Sovyonok' and met the girls from the camp in the real world. But it's New Year at hand! And it needs to be celebrated! 'Frosty Kiss' is a tiny piece of this holiday that will bring back the well-loved characters of the novel one more time, even if it lasts only for a few moments. But somewhere deep in your heart should always be a place for celebration and feelings left by a kiss in the most important night of the year.
